item.title: Whats this error?
item.dc:creator: @Kono-chan Kono-chan
item.description:
@Kono-chan wrote:

T1 errors are generally when the server is sending a packet to the client that the client does not have.

T2 is generally an error with a packet that the client DOES have.

Read full topic
